title: Epic Win Presents: The Heroes Cabaret!
desc:
An Epic Win production, this Cabaret will feature local and national performers as we band together to raise funds for the Heroes Project, a charity devoted to bringing terminally ill children to conventions in cosplay.? Featured Performers: (more to come) 
 Kent Axell (mentalist, cosplay consultant) www.kentaxell.com Stacey Weiland (cosplayer) https://www.facebook.com/NegativeStacey/ Andrew Sklar (Actor and cosplayer, Nationally touring performer) Tom Catt (Cosplayer and Drag performer)  www.facebook.com/tomcattofficial
